defining_moments.title: The Calculus Club Conundrum
defining_moments.description: Leading the calculus club, I faced a revolt when members struggled with complex integrals. By fostering a collaborative environment, I learned to adapt my leadership style and embrace diverse problem-solving approaches.

defining_moments.title: Graphing My Way to Understanding
defining_moments.description: Struggling with calculus graphs, I created a visual study guide that transformed my understanding. This process taught me the value of visual learning and creative problem-solving.

defining_moments.title: The Calculus Test Failure
defining_moments.description: After failing a crucial calculus test, I sought help from my teacher and peers, which led to a breakthrough in my understanding. This experience taught me humility and the importance of seeking help.
